      },
      "startTime": 226.2000027615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr021.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんの真似をしてたって話をした時は\n「私にも見せて」ってすっごく迫られましたけど",
